{"tid":1786632,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本港最新失業率升至3.2%　飲食業達6.2%八年來最高","createTime":"2019-12-17T09:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T10:13:14.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0597bb975a0df51cf5a5672425832f1220778857","tid":1786632,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:24:50.000Z","msg":"本港失業率上升，政府統計處公布，9至11月整體失業率升至3.2%，較上月公布上升0.1個百分點。受到本地社會事件嚴重打擊，與消費及旅遊相關的零售、住宿及飲食業，影響最嚴重，失業率進一步上升至5.2%，是三年來高位，當中飲食業更升至6.2%，是超過八年來的最高水平。<br />\n<br />\n就業不足率維持在1.2%，受影響行業包括樓房裝飾、修葺及保養業，及餐飲服務活動業。勞工及福利局長羅致光表示，經濟情況繼續惡化，令勞工市場進一步放緩，倘若整體經濟繼續轉弱，勞工市場在短期內將會面對更大壓力，政府會密切留意有關發展。"},{"pid":"5b278a1e05096cfe21d5fce9c42e5b870c3b7a31","tid":1786632,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:24:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1239384&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1239384%26csid%3D261_341&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0qd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=ead6af34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1239384&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"967fe36aa11f2532f05541731052735f48764041","tid":1786632,"uid":291309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:13:14.000Z","msg":"政府誤導<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oocBmd3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoocBmd3.jpg&h=5948954c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}